params._newOwner: The address to transfer ownership to.

addHardLink(address,uint256).notice: This function has alos the purpose to allow future proof linking. If the contracts change a lot in future iterations this is a way to link contracts even if they are not linkable any more by addLink standards.

renounceOwnership().notice: Renouncing to ownership will leave the contract without an owner. It will not be possible to call the functions with the `onlyOwner` modifier anymore.
